Class SGFingerInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • SecuGen.FDxSDKPro.jni.SGFingerInfo

  • public class SGFingerInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains information about a fingerprint sample in an ANSI378 or ISO19794 template.
